---
title: Caribbean Style Spiced Double Prawns with Charred Corn and Kiwi Salsa
description: Flavoured with jerk seasoning that contains paprika, cayenne, pimento and thyme, our Caribbean Style Spiced Double Prawns are paired with a zingy kiwi salsa for extra freshness and some Caribbean sunshine.
